		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this activity, the core team will diagram community connections to provide a foundation for a community engagement plan.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="This activity will help capture the social network in your community so that you can identify and address gaps in engagement. For example, the activity will guide you through documenting how people get their information, how resources are distributed and shared, and how organizations are connected.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="The core team will meet to ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="Diagram Community Connections"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch2_DiagramCommunityConnections.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=". We recommend building on the Community Connections Table completed in first activity. The team will draw out specific relationships between community members/organizations.">
			</text>
